<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="coast-n">coast <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /kəʊst/    美 /koʊst/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 海岸；海滨：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Why not take them for a walk along the coast?
为什么不带他们沿着海边散散步呢？</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="on-the-coast">on the coast</h3>
<p>1.<strong>在海岸上：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Barcelona is a city on the coast of Spain.
巴塞罗那是一座西班牙的海滨城市。</p><footer>外研③ – 1</footer></div>

<h3 id="off-the-coast">off the coast</h3>
<p>1.<strong>在沿岸的海面上：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There are many islands off the coast.
沿海有许多岛屿。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>coastal /'kəʊstl/ adj   </p></div>